OL,3,CRicky Hatton's son says tribute night
OL,4,Cwill make sure dad's 'legacy will live
OL,5,Con'
OL,7,FRicky Hatton's son Campbell spoke
OL,8,Fexclusively to ITV News' Mike Hall
OL,9,Fabout his father, Tyson Fury, and a
OL,10,Fcharity boxing night.
OL,12,FRicky Hatton's son has said his dad
OL,13,F"wouldn't have done anything
OL,14,Fdifferent" in his career ahead of a
OL,15,Ftribute event to remember the late
OL,16,Fboxer.
OL,18,FThe 46-year-old, described as a doting
OL,19,Ffather, was found dead at his at home
OL,20,Fin Hyde, Greater Manchester on Sunday
OL,21,F14 September.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1776276666
OL,3,CRicky Hatton's son says tribute night
OL,4,Cwill make sure dad's 'legacy will live
OL,5,Con'
OL,7,FAn inquest into his death heard it was
OL,8,Fnot clear the former boxer intended to
OL,9,Ftake his own life, and post-mortem
OL,10,Fevidence showed some brain damage
OL,11,Fcaused by repeated head injuries
OL,12,Fcommonly found in contact sports.
OL,14,FHatton's son Campbell told ITV News
OL,15,Fthat his father's passing has not
OL,16,Faffected his potential return to
OL,17,Fboxing.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1776276666
OL,3,CRicky Hatton's son says tribute night
OL,4,Cwill make sure dad's 'legacy will live
OL,5,Con'
OL,7,FHe said: "We do know the risk going
OL,8,Finto it and I think if you'd have been
OL,9,Fable to ask my dad that question now I
OL,10,Fdon't think he'd have done anything
OL,11,Fdifferent."
OL,13,FA Las Vegas themed tribute night is
OL,14,Fset to take place in Manchester in
OL,15,FJune called 'Evening4Ricky', to
OL,16,Fremember and celebrate his life.
OL,18,FCampbell said: "There's already been
OL,19,Fso many great tribute to my dad so far
OL,20,Fand there's still more to come.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1776276666
OL,3,CRicky Hatton's son says tribute night
OL,4,Cwill make sure dad's 'legacy will live
OL,5,Con'
OL,7,F"There's going to be a lot of famous
OL,8,Ffaces there and a lot of people who my
OL,9,Fdad knew as well so it should be a
OL,10,Fgood night. It would be great to see
OL,11,Feveryone down there, I'm sure it will
OL,12,Fbe an emotional one."
OL,14,FHe said the event will be a happy
OL,15,Fcelebration for his dad, but he's sad
OL,16,Fthat Hatton will not be there to see
OL,17,Fit.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1776276666
OL,3,CRicky Hatton's son says tribute night
OL,4,Cwill make sure dad's 'legacy will live
OL,5,Con'
OL,7,FHatton's good friend Tyson Fury paid
OL,8,Ftribute to him in his comeback fight
OL,9,Fon Saturday 11 April, where he beat
OL,10,FArslanbek Makmudov.
OL,12,FFury's gloves - coloured light blue
OL,13,Ffor Hatton's beloved Manchester City -
OL,14,Fsaid "there's only one Ricky Hatton".
OL,15,FHis shorts also had "RIP Ricky" sewn
OL,16,Finto the back, in the same light blue,
OL,17,Fand he walked to the ring with 'Blue
OL,18,FMoon' playing.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1776276666
OL,3,CRicky Hatton's son says tribute night
OL,4,Cwill make sure dad's 'legacy will live
OL,5,Con'
OL,7,FCampbell said: "It was a nice surprise
OL,8,Fto see everything he did with the
OL,9,Fshorts, the ring walk and the speech
OL,10,Fafterwards as well, it was another
OL,11,Flevel.
OL,13,F"I can't thank Tyson enough, he was a
OL,14,Fgood mate of my dad's and they went on
OL,15,Fa nice journey with Tyson's comeback
OL,16,Ftogether so it meant a lot to us as a
OL,17,Ffamily."
OL,19,FCampbell has also hinted at a return
OL,20,Fto boxing, despite the findings of the
OL,21,Finquest into his dad's death.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1776276666
OL,3,CRicky Hatton's son says tribute night
OL,4,Cwill make sure dad's 'legacy will live
OL,5,Con'
OL,7,FHatton was found to have chronic
OL,8,Ftraumatic encephalopathy (CTE), a type
OL,9,Fof brain damage likely caused by his
OL,10,Flife in the ring.
OL,12,FAn expert told the inquest it was rare
OL,13,Fto find in someone of his age, and was
OL,14,Fusually only found in older people
OL,15,Fwith Alzheimers.
OL,17,FCampbell said the news was not a
OL,18,Fshock, as he had noticed his dad's
OL,19,Fmemory getting worse in recent years,
OL,20,Fbut it would not stop him from getting
OL,21,Fback in the ring.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1776276666
OL,3,CRicky Hatton's son says tribute night
OL,4,Cwill make sure dad's 'legacy will live
OL,5,Con'
OL,7,FHe said "I think maybe we could do a
OL,8,Flittle bit more in regards to
OL,9,Fsupporting fighters and letting them
OL,10,Fknow the risks because it is something
OL,11,Fthat does get overlooked.
OL,13,F"Maybe there's more we could be doing
OL,14,Fbut I definitely wouldn't have changed
OL,15,Fanything."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
